description:
Thor started out as a concept band in 1973. They were first called "Centaur" and then "Mikl Body Rock". These entities were the brainchild of Jon Mikl, a vocalist, musician and body building champion who won titles such as Mr. USA and Mr. Canada. He decided to combine Muscle with Music.

Several comics were made about the hard rocking Thor, who's still rocking in 2014.
name: Thor
